('ONET-CYTOGENETIC_TECHNOLOGISTS', 'source_onet_cytogenetic_technologists', 'Cytogenetic Technologists', 'Cytogenetic Technologists is an imported ONET role/occupation concept. It needs TALLENTIN normalization before production routing.', 'role_title', 'Analyze chromosomes or chromosome segments found in biological specimens, such as amniotic fluids, bone marrow, solid tumors, and blood to aid in the study, diagnosis, classification, or treatment of inherited or acquired genetic diseases. Conduct analyses through classical cytogenetic, fluorescent in situ hybridization (FISH) or array comparative genome hybridization (aCGH) techniques.', ARRAY['Certified Cytogenetic Technologist','Clinical Cytogeneticist Scientist (CCS)','Cytogenetic Technician','Cytogenetic Technologist','Cytogenetics Clinical Laboratory Specialist (CG CLSp)','Cytogenetics Technical Specialist','Cytogenetics Technologist','Cytologist','Cytotechnician','Flow Cytometry Specialist','Flow Cytometry Technologist','Genetic Technologist','Laboratory Specialist (Lab Specialist)','Laboratory Technologist (Lab Technologist)','Medical Laboratory Scientist (MLS)','Medical Technologist (MT)','Molecular Genetics Technologist','Research Laboratory Specialist (Research Lab Specialist)']::text[], ARRAY['Cytogenetic Technologists','Certified Cytogenetic Technologist','Clinical Cytogeneticist Scientist (CCS)','Cytogenetic Technician','Cytogenetic Technologist','Cytogenetics Clinical Laboratory Specialist (CG CLSp)','Cytogenetics Technical Specialist','Cytogenetics Technologist','Cytologist','Cytotechnician','Flow Cytometry Specialist','Flow Cytometry Technologist','Genetic Technologist','Laboratory Specialist (Lab Specialist)','Laboratory Technologist (Lab Technologist)','Medical Laboratory Scientist (MLS)','Medical Technologist (MT)','Molecular Genetics Technologist','Research Laboratory Specialist (Research Lab Specialist)']::text[], ARRAY['Reading Comprehension','Active Listening','Writing','Speaking','Mathematics